 Mailpit tracks\n  mailpit:open        Open the running Mailpit dashboard\n  mail:install        Install a Mailpit track\n  mail:update         Update installed Mailpit tracks\n  mail:uninstall      Uninstall a Mailpit track\n  mail:list           List installed Mailpit tracks\n  mail:open           Open the running Mailpit dashboard\n  redis:install       Install a Redis track\n  redis:update        Update installed Redis tracks\n  redis:uninstall     Uninstall a Redis track\n  redis:list          List installed Redis tracks\n  rustfs:install      Install a RustFS track\n  rustfs:update       Update installed RustFS tracks\n  rustfs:uninstall    Uninstall a RustFS track\n  rustfs:list         List installed RustFS tracks\n  rustfs:open         Open the running RustFS console\n  s3:install          Install a RustFS track (S3 alias)\n  s3:update           Update installed RustFS tracks (S3 alias)\n  s3:uninstall        Uninstall a RustFS track (S3 alias)\n  s3:list             List installed RustFS tracks (S3 alias)\n  s3:open             Open the running RustFS console (S3 alias)\n  mysql:install       Install a MySQL track\n  mysql:update        Update installed MySQL tracks\n  mysql:uninstall     Uninstall a MySQL track\n  mysql:list          List installed MySQL tracks\n  postgres:install    Install a Postgres track\n  postgres:update     Update installed Postgres tracks\n  postgres:uninstall  Uninstall a Postgres track\n  postgres:list       List installed Postgres tracks\n  pg:install          Install a Postgres track\n  pg:update           Update installed Postgres tracks\n  pg:uninstall        Uninstall a Postgres track\n  pg:list             List installed Postgres tracks\n\nOptions:\n      --no-color  Disable colored output\n  -h, --help      Print help\n  -V, --version   Print version\n",
